										<h2>
											<a href="http://www.sourcememory.net/veleda/?p=521" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Notre Dame de la Vie II: Savior of Infants">Notre Dame de la Vie II: Savior of Infants</a>
										</h2>
																				<div class="metabar">
											<em>
												
																								<span class="sword">by</span> <span class="post-author vcard"><a href="http://www.sourcememory.net/veleda/?author=1">Veleda</a></span>

																								
																									<span class="sword">on</span> <abbr title="2012-04-23" class="published">April 23, 2012</abbr>
																								
																								&middot;												<a rel="nofollow" class="comments-num" href="http://www.sourcememory.net/veleda/?p=521#comments" title="View Comments">No Comments</a>
																								
																								
