								</div>
																		<div class="post-excerpt">
											<p>Saving the babies: fountain goddesses and respite baptism Another amazing aspect of the ancient sanctuary of Notre Dame de la Vie was as a compassionate place of refuge from harmful religious dogma. It became a sanctuaire de répit, or &#8220;respite sanctuary.&#8221; Respite from what? &#8211;from the church doctrine of eternal damnation of those who died [...]</p>
										</div>

